title: How do I delete the fingerprints registered on my phone?
answer:
Go to Settings > Fingerprint ID > Fingerprint management and enter the unlock password. Select the fingerprints you want to delete in the fingerprint list and touch Delete. 

 You can also access the phone using the owner password. Go to Settings > Security > Privacy protection and enter the owner password. Touch Manage fingerprints and check all the fingerprints registered in owner mode and visitor mode.
